        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The number of AI generations you get per month depends on your plan. The Core plan includes 10 AI generations per month. The Plus plan bumps that to 100. The Ultimate plan offers 500.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What I appreciate about this approach is that the AI tools are not replacing the library — they are adding to it. You might find the perfect stock photo for 80% of your projects, but for that last 20% where you need something hyper-specific, the AI tools fill the gap. No need to jump to another platform.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l4",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/envato-elements-new-features"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Want to stay updated on what is new? Bookmark our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Envato Elements new features page",
            "marks": [
              "l4"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
