      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "New and Highlighted Features",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Envato Elements keeps evolving. Here are some of the standout features and recent additions that deserve attention:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Lifetime Commercial License",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Every asset you download — including AI-generated content — comes with a lifetime commercial license. Use it in client projects, YouTube videos, paid ads, merchandise, print materials, and more. No attribution required for most assets.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Unlimited Downloads, No Caps",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "There is no download limit. No daily cap. No credits system. If you need 500 assets in a month, download 500 assets. This single feature is what makes Envato Elements exceptional value compared to per-asset pricing models.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Single-Use Licenses with Multi-Project Flexibility",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Each download is licensed for use in one end product (one client project, one video, one product). If you need the same asset for a second project, just download it again from your history — still unlimited, still free within your subscription.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Organized Collections & Curated Sets",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The editorial team curates themed collections that make it easier to discover assets. Seasonal collections, trending styles, and industry-specific bundles help you find what you need faster.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Seamless Integrations",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Many templates are built specifically for tools you already use: Premiere Pro, After Effects, Photoshop, Illustrator, Figma, Canva, Keynote, PowerPoint, and more. You download a template, open it in your tool, and customize. No conversion headaches.",
            "marks": []
