      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Envato Elements is a subscription service that gives you unlimited downloads of over 28 million creative assets — stock photos, video, music, templates, fonts, graphics, and AI tools. You pay one monthly or annual fee, download as many assets as you need, and receive a lifetime commercial license on every download.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can I use Envato Elements assets for commercial projects?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. Every asset you download from Envato Elements — including AI-generated content — comes with a lifetime commercial license. You can use the assets in client projects, YouTube videos, paid advertisements, merchandise, and print materials. No attribution is required for most assets.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How much does Envato Elements cost?",
