      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Envato Elements offers three plans: Core at $16.50/month (billed annually) with 10 AI generations, Plus at $39/month (billed annually) with 100 AI generations, and Ultimate at $109/month (billed annually) with 500 AI generations. All plans include unlimited downloads of 28M+ creative assets and a lifetime commercial license.",
